# Screen Wakelock Detector — project rules

@AGENTS.md is **required reading** every session.

## FOSS and security

- Apache-2.0; F-Droid-only distribution
- **No `INTERNET` permission** in release manifest
- No Firebase, Play Services, proprietary analytics, or non-OSI Gradle deps
- New dependencies: check [`docs/FOSS.md`](docs/FOSS.md); update AGENT_MEMORY

## Material Design 3 only

- Use `androidx.compose.material3` — **never** `androidx.compose.material` (M2)
- Follow [`docs/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md`](docs/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md)
- Dynamic color API 31+; static fallback 29–30
- Expressive APIs opt-in only; never block release on alpha

## Milestone workflow

- Work from [`docs/BUILD_PLAN.md`](docs/BUILD_PLAN.md) labels: AGENT / ADB / HUMAN
- Spawn **parallel subagents** for `<!-- PARALLEL -->` blocks (see AGENTS.md)
- **Run until milestone complete** — do not stop after one task
- Gate checklists in [`docs/GATES.md`](docs/GATES.md) before marking milestone done

## Validate before push

Never push without:

1. `./gradlew lint test assembleDebug` (when app module exists)
2. Applicable gate checklist items
3. **`scripts/smoke/m{N}_smoke.sh` exit 0** before archive
4. CHANGELOG `[Unreleased]` + AGENT_MEMORY updated

## Smoke before archive

- **Never** run `archive-completed-tasks.py` without smoke PASS in GATES.md
- Record: `Smoke M{N}: PASS <timestamp> <serial> <version>`

## Git

- Lead agent only commits/pushes per milestone
- Do not start M(N+1) until M(N) gate passed and pushed to GitLab

## Root

- libsu in-app only; command allowlist — no user input in shell
- Document in [`docs/ROOT.md`](docs/ROOT.md)

## Do not edit

- Plan files in uploads/ or external `.plan.md` sources — use BUILD_PLAN.md instead
